  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IridaSequenceFile, IridaThing, MutableIridaThing, RemoteSynchronizable, Timestamped<Long>, VersionedFileFields<Long>, Comparable<SequenceFile>
    @Entity
public class SequenceFile
extends IridaResourceSupport
implements MutableIridaThing, Comparable<SequenceFile>, VersionedFileFields<Long>, IridaSequenceFile, RemoteSynchronizable
    A file that may be stored somewhere on the file system and belongs to a particular Sample.

      • getUploadSha256

        public String getUploadSha256()
        Get the sha256 checksum for a file when it was uploaded. NOTE: This checksum may not be the same as the sha256 for the current file. The checksum from the originally uploaded file is saved so an uploader can verify its file upload.
        Returns:
        the string sha256 for the uploaded file.
